resultList.Query:
SELECT DISTINCT
	[mp].[FK_Machines] AS [FK_Machines],
	[mp].[PK_MachineModulePaths] AS [FK_MachineModulePaths]           
FROM
	[dbo].[mocAutoruns] AS [ar] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[MachinesToEvaluate] AS [me] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([me].[RK_Machines] = [ar].[FK_Machines])
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[Paths] AS [pa] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([pa].[PK_Paths] = [ar].[FK_Paths__RegistryPath])
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[MachineModulePaths] AS [mp] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([mp].[PK_MachineModulePaths] = [ar].[FK_MachineModulePaths] AND [mp].[FK_Machines] = [ar].[FK_Machines])
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[Modules] AS [mo] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([mo].[PK_Modules] = [mp].[FK_Modules])
WHERE 
	[ar].[Type] = 22 AND 
	[mo].[ModuleSignaturePresent] = 0 AND
	[ar].[MarkedAsDeleted] = 0
resultList.Name: Autorun_Unsigned_ServiceDLL.sql

resultList.Query:
DECLARE @DATE_THRESHOLD AS SMALLDATETIME = DATEADD(MONTH, -1, GETUTCDATE());

SELECT DISTINCT
	[mp].[FK_Machines] AS [FK_Machines],
	[mp].[PK_MachineModulePaths] AS [FK_MachineModulePaths]           
FROM
	[dbo].[MachineModulePaths] AS [mp] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[Modules] AS [mo] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([mo].[PK_Modules] = [mp].[FK_Modules])
WHERE 
	[mo].[PEUTCTimeDateStamp] > @DATE_THRESHOLD AND
	[mo].[PEUTCTimeDateStamp] <= GETUTCDATE() AND
	[mp].[MarkedAsDeleted]  = 0
resultList.Name: Compiled_In_Last_Month.sql

resultList.Query:
SELECT DISTINCT
	[mp].[FK_Machines] AS [FK_Machines],
	[mp].[PK_MachineModulePaths] AS [FK_MachineModulePaths]           
FROM
	[dbo].[MachineModulePaths] AS [mp] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE 
	[mp].[FilenameUTCTimeCreated] >= DATEADD(MONTH, -1, GETUTCDATE()) AND
	[mp].[FilenameUTCTimeCreated] <= GETUTCDATE() AND
	[mp].[MarkedAsDeleted] = 0
resultList.Name: Created_In_Last_Month.sql

resultList.Query:
SELECT DISTINCT
	[mp].[FK_Machines] AS [FK_Machines],
	[mp].[PK_MachineModulePaths] AS [FK_MachineModulePaths]           
FROM
	[dbo].[MachineModulePaths] AS [mp] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[MachinesToEvaluate] AS [me] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([me].[RK_Machines] = [mp].[FK_Machines])
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[Modules] AS [mo] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([mo].[PK_Modules] = [mp].[FK_Modules])
WHERE 
	[mo].[Description] = '' AND
	(
		[mo].[ModulePE32] = 1 OR
		[mo].[ModulePE64] = 1
	) AND
	[mp].[MarkedAsDeleted]  = 0
resultList.Name: No_File_Description.sql

resultList.Query:
SELECT DISTINCT
	[mp].[FK_Machines] AS [FK_Machines],
	[mp].[PK_MachineModulePaths] AS [FK_MachineModulePaths]           
FROM
	[dbo].[MachineModulePaths] AS [mp] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[MachinesToEvaluate] AS [me] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([me].[RK_Machines] = [mp].[FK_Machines])
WHERE 
	[mp].[FileDirectoryHiddenAttributes] = 1 AND
	[mp].[MarkedAsDeleted]  = 0
resultList.Name: Directory_Hidden.sql

resultList.Query:
DECLARE @LASTIOCEVAL AS DATETIME2 = (SELECT ISNULL(LastIOCEvaluationUTCTime, CONVERT(DATETIME, 0)) FROM dbo.ApplicationSetup)

SELECT DISTINCT
	[mp].[FK_Machines] AS [FK_Machines],
	[mp].[PK_MachineModulePaths] AS [FK_MachineModulePaths]
FROM
	[dbo].[mocSentinelEvents] AS [se] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[MachinesToEvaluate] AS [me] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([me].[RK_Machines] = [se].[FK_Machines])
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[MachineModulePaths] AS [mp] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([mp].[PK_MachineModulePaths] = [se].[FK_MachineModulePaths])
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[FileNames] AS [fn] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([fn].[PK_FileNames] = [se].[FK_FileNames__TargetProcessImageFileName])
WHERE 
	[se].[BehaviorProcessCreateProcess] = 1 AND
	[se].[AuditUTCDate] > @LASTIOCEVAL AND
	[fn].[FileName] = N'SC.EXE' AND
	[mp].[FK_Modules] != -1 AND
	[mp].[MarkedAsDeleted] = 0 -- Testing MarkedAsDeleted on MP instead of SE for Events
resultList.Name: Runs_SC.sql

resultList.Query:
DECLARE @LASTIOCEVAL AS DATETIME2 = (SELECT ISNULL(LastIOCEvaluationUTCTime, CONVERT(DATETIME, 0)) FROM dbo.ApplicationSetup)

SELECT DISTINCT
	[mp].[FK_Machines] AS [FK_Machines],
	[mp].[PK_MachineModulePaths] AS [FK_MachineModulePaths]
FROM
	[dbo].[mocSentinelEvents] AS [se] WITH(NOLOCK)
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[MachinesToEvaluate] AS [me] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([me].[RK_Machines] = [se].[FK_Machines])
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[MachineModulePaths] AS [mp] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([mp].[PK_MachineModulePaths] = [se].[FK_MachineModulePaths])
	INNER JOIN [dbo].[FileNames] AS [fn] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([fn].[PK_FileNames] = [se].[FK_FileNames__TargetProcessImageFileName])
WHERE 
	[se].[BehaviorProcessCreateProcess] = 1 AND
	[se].[AuditUTCDate] > @LASTIOCEVAL AND
	[fn].[FileName] = N'SCHTASKS.EXE' AND
	[mp].[FK_Modules] != -1 AND
	[mp].[MarkedAsDeleted] = 0 -- Testing MarkedAsDeleted on MP instead of SE for Events
resultList.Name: Runs_SCHTASKS.sql
